# Analytics & Privacy

Follow existing patterns in `scripts/analytics.js`.

## Events
Use `EILLON_ANALYTICS.track(name, props)` — production Vercel WA only.

## Never in events or UTMs
Email · name · phone · user ids · free-text form values

## UTM
Standard five params; see `/growth/utm-system.md`. Persist via waitlist API only as implemented.

## Forms
Preserve consent/honeypot patterns on `[data-waitlist-form]`. No new third-party trackers without human review.

## Docs
`/docs/growth-measurement.md` for KPI definitions.
